{"type": "article", "id": 23266, "title": "新秀丽完成TUMI收购，以及，蕾哈娜和Manolo Blahnik出联名系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-03-04T10:12:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1581, "name": "Chloe"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 3250, "name": "Rick Owens"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 24391, "name": "YUUL YIE"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 24392, "name": "Anglepoise"}, {"id": 5438, "name": "Dolce & Gabbana"}, {"id": 18988, "name": "TUMI"}, {"id": 2382, "name": "新秀丽"}, {"id": 12467, "name": "蕾哈娜"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133919dHqFDlR1gYewAiWT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/adidas-full-year-net-profit-10368441/\">Adidas 去年四季度表现强劲</a>｜</b>Adidas 财报显示至去年 12 月 31 日的三个月内，净收入增长了 68.7%，令四季度净亏损从 1.39 亿欧元收窄至 4400 万欧元（约合 4820 万美元），尽管行销上的花费也比去年同期高出 31%。依靠西欧、大中华和拉丁美洲市场的增长拉动，全年净收入上涨了 29% 至 6.4 亿欧元（约合 7.106 亿美元）。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Moncler-2015-core-profit-up-29-pct-sales-growth-slows,664839.html#.VtjgaIS9rBI\">Moncler 2015 核心利润增加 29%</a>｜</b>去年 Moncler 的收益增长了 19％，但在刚刚过去的几个月里增速又开始放缓，只因为这个冬季异常温暖以及中国市场的较弱表现。销售额增长了 27% 至 8.8 亿欧元（约合 9.63 亿美元），超过市场预期的 8.68 亿欧元。可比商店销售额增长了 6%，全年的核心利润增长了 29％。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/financial/hong-kong-retail-sales-drop-6-5-in-january-10377870/\">香港零售业仍然在下跌</a> |</b> 香港统计局周四傍晚发布 1 月份零售业数据，1 月份香港零售业总销售额下跌 6.5%，较 2015 年 12 月的 8.5% 的跌幅有所收窄。其中珠宝首饰、钟表及名贵礼品 1 月销售跌幅 16.3%；服装销售下跌 4.9%；百货公司物品下跌 3.6%；药物及化妆品下跌 3.6%；眼镜店销售下跌 6.3%；只有鞋类销售有 5.7% 的回升。</p>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-images-wide\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/tom-tailor-opens-store-on-jd-com-10377849/\">又一个国际品牌进驻京东</a> | </b>Tom Tailor 是一个来自德国汉堡的运动品牌，京东是其在中国的第一家网上零售店，目前在中国有 15 家零售店，包括去年 11 月在上海新开的一家。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/samsonite-acqure-tumi-in-1-8-billion-cash-deal-10379573/\">新秀丽要以 18 亿美元收购 Tumi</a> |</b> Tumi 是美国轻奢箱包品牌，此前市场估值为 14 亿美元，新秀丽的首席执行官表示，未来将扩大 Tumi 在亚洲和欧洲的市场。</p>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-images-wide\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/life-style/fashion/dolce-gabbana-release-offensive-slave-sandal-article-1.2551821\">Dolce &amp; Gabbana 有双凉鞋叫做“奴隶鞋”</a>| </b>这件事情又引起了公愤。这类事情已经不是第一次了，两位设计师总是分不清楚消费者的情绪痛点，之前就有因为同性恋话题引发过风波。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133856Arve80NQwa1O3ngo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72283465\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>这里有一些来自巴黎时装周的 T 台照片，我们选了一些你必须要知道的系列。</p>\n<p class=\"\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\n<p class=\"\">Vetements<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133856t8fyX0NzAb9wsarZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.05555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Lanvin<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133857dSg0yDA9fxhL5eHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"4.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Rick Owens<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133858sagJ1Xqb5mF9VNuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"4.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Balmain<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071338581exojPKa63FC9SJk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.81944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Chloé<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133859M5IYBGfDh8ClJTgv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.81944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>adidas Originals by White Mountaineering 2016 春夏联名</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133900fewk6KSAFPcBTY8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133900zTYf5gyIU3jrxn2D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133901a5xNwmK8hZUAigr9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133901DABVjPgZec1a5kwT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">EVISU 联手 3125c 打造全新限定系列。由陈冠希主理的 3125c 为 EVISU 融入中国传统设计元素，将唐装与牛仔衣融合；其余单品也有不少中国味。该系列将于 3 月 12 日在 EVISU 专柜正式发售。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133902Wr6cRdG8BjSqhyak.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071339022BwiUszlWYq4AoH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133903YhPiR1pz89AVg2Qn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Rihanna 与传奇鞋履设计师 Manolo Blahnik 合作一个限量系列，共六款，将于 5 月 5 日在 Blahnik 的纽约、伦敦和香港门店上市，单宁、亮片和珠宝装饰。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071339038aKoTjxfsXdGZSAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133904ED0oZIf5vmQAGB7z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09129213\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133904648WZduM0sKzCxpX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09129213\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133905XHVGy82UD04rIckp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133905Mpuko0geNnmZl3Fr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33286517\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">就不爱穿细高跟的女生们，这里有一个来自首尔的女鞋品牌 <a href=\"http://www.yuulyieshop.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">YUUL YIE</a>，梯形粗跟是它的招牌，强烈硬实的皮革选色与环扣造型设计显得比较有街头感。近年在首尔、东京与香港逐渐展开知名度，也受到韩国各大时装杂志的搭配拍摄。喜欢粗跟的不妨看看。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133906DH1n2zK3O9mvwLhU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66526316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133906F2EvaIhoiyZO5Xl3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66526316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071339078au6okXsMDOmQ0N2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66526316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133907aqyep1gJXxEILoj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133908bc7DHk3yCE9OnLXl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133909KnQk2gIPBFtGJdjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66526316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Dee &amp; Ricky 和 PUMA 的联名系列，售价 110 美元，目前可以在<a href=\"http://www.featuresneakerboutique.com/collections/puma\">这里</a>买到。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133909IATN64MSJu7VjhHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133910cKAEdtoU6Fhkz17Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这是一个来自瑞典斯德哥尔摩的 Alexis Holm 所创立的生活时尚品牌 squarestreet，最新 SQ31 黑银配色铝制腕表选用自 1909 年创立的瑞士知名品牌 Ronda 机芯，表盘由外至内共有三个时间刻度，值得一提的是最外层的分钟，每格都有提供数字方便查看。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133910XYRpErdeMPmSiCqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713391131MohyiROq6w0Ln4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133911OwDrYtagHljbCZuv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133912dDOmLQEn0Zi8qA3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">有一个布鲁克林的摄影师叫做 Geordie Wood，他的作品看起来像是时尚摄影，但又有点像社论式的城市记录。他曾为大牌时装拍摄，也为纽约时报、Vogue、Rolling Stone 等提供照片。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133912hB8jkoqVgWIlyJYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64081146\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071339137N02l48Bc6i5y9sX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6427718\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133914jWdAnGy7rJNK1OUg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6528436\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133914KqvLgckibhrpjEI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33287293\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133915YftXiSUgIEsec7BQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33287293\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"> Anglepoise 为了庆祝其一百周年，发布了几款超大号“台灯”，都是以其最受欢迎的台灯为原型，直接放大三倍来售卖。所有的灯都是在英国手工制造，在室内室外都可以使用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133915bOe7sWaG4MzjVoqi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65830346\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133916k5eMLXpBQoI3Og26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133916FhKLOj9vSRgfb54E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65830346\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133917XH2mUesAGj6ROWu9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65830346\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133917FzYNyu2U9mKliZMH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65830346\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133918UVDcQLKmbXTxi0s6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65830346\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}